title: Vince Flynn, Kyle Mills - Mitch Rapp [1 - 14]
description:
Mitch Rapp is a counter-terrorism operative employed, first unofficially then officially, by the CIA. The primary focus of the character is thwarting Middle Eastern terrorist attacks on the United States and he is presented as an aggressive operative who is willing to take measures that are more extreme than might be considered commonly acceptable.


1999 Transfer of Power
2000 The Third Option
2001 Separation of Power
2003 Executive Power
2004 Memorial Day
2005 Consent to Kill
2006 Act of Treason
2007 Protect and Defend
2008 Extreme Measures
2009 Pursuit of Honor
2010 American Assassin
2012 Kill Shot
2012 The Last Man
2015 The Survivor


Read by George Guidall, Nick Sullivan (#3 & #4) Ken Kliban (#5)
Format: MP3
Bitrate: 32 Kbps
Unabridged
